    "This predicament cannot be ameliorated through moral persuasion alone; it demands the establishment of legally binding regulations endowed with coercive authority.",
    "Thirdly, the content of these AI ethical guidelines tends to remain abstract and theoretical (Cheng, Han and Nasirov 2024; Cheng and Liu 2023).",
